==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Come-along
<hw>Come"-a*long`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A gripping device, as for
stretching wire, etc., consisting of two jaws so attached to a ring that
they are closed by pulling on the ring.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Co-meddle</ent>⟦br⟧
